overview: In front of Yoon-ju, who is working as a stewardess, a middle school alumni official comes to visit after 10 years.  A set meal that appeared in such a wonderful shape that it was impossible to find it in its former form.  Yoon-ju tries to reject her formality, saying that he is already married, but in the face of her constant temptation, she eventually collapses at her helplessness...
title: Going Out 2
